                                                  9.6.<?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170421T110839+0200" comment="{{Br. 119.17–36}}"?>1866<?oxy_comment_end?></ref>.</note></seg></p><closer>For the Directors<lb/>John Weston</closer><postscript><p>any further delay will be fatal </p></postscript></div></body></text></TEI>